## Guardrails
- Run attribution monthly minimum — quarterly is too infrequent to catch signal decay early
- Minimum 50 trades per segment before drawing conclusions from segment-level data
- Never act on a single month of attribution data — look for 3-month trends
- Attribution findings that suggest parameter changes must go to QR, not be implemented directly
